- [GoRouter 公式ドキュメント](https://pub.dev/packages/go_router)
- [Flutter ナビゲーションガイド](https://docs.flutter.dev/ui/navigation)
- [GoRouter と Riverpod の統合](https://codewithandrea.com/articles/flutter-navigation-gorouter-riverpod/)
- [StatefulShellRoute の使い方](https://pub.dev/documentation/go_router/latest/go_router/StatefulShellRoute-class.html)

